              <!-- Panel 1: The Process -->
              <div id="faqpanel1" class="faq-panel">
                <details class="faq-item" open>
                  <summary>How does the process work from start to finish? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Simple and transparent. We start with a free 30-minute strategy call to understand your business and goals. Once the contract is signed we start immediately — no waiting, no delays. The build runs as a focused 3-week sprint with full visibility at every stage.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>What do you need from me to get started? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Just the basics — your business goals, target audience, and any branding you already have such as a logo, colors, or photos. We will contact you for any additional information we need along the way. No branding yet? We can handle that too as part of our branding service.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Will I be involved during the build? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Yes, and your involvement makes the difference. We share progress at every stage of the design — header, footer, sections — as each part is completed. To keep the project moving on schedule, we ask that you review each finished stage promptly and provide your feedback before we move to the next one. This keeps us inside the 3-week timeline and avoids delays on both sides.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>What if I already have a website? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">We will audit it first. If it has a solid foundation we can redesign and optimize it. If it is holding your business back we will recommend a full rebuild and tell you exactly why.</p>
                </details>
              </div>

              <!-- Panel 2: Design & Performance -->
              <div id="faqpanel2" class="faq-panel">
                <details class="faq-item" open>
                  <summary>Will my website be custom or template-based? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">We prefer building fully custom websites tailored to your brand and goals — that is how we deliver the best results. In some cases, if a template strictly fits your requirements and budget, we can work with one. We will always recommend the approach that serves your business best and be transparent about which direction we are taking.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>How fast will my website load? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">For custom-built static sites and landing pages we guarantee under 2 seconds. For WooCommerce e-commerce builds we target 2.5 to 3 seconds or less. Speed depends on the project requirements — page length, features, and content — but we guarantee we will always do our best to deliver the fastest possible result for your specific build.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Will my website work on mobile? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Every layout starts at mobile. We design for the phone in your customer's hand first, then scale up to tablet and desktop. Mobile-first is not optional — it is how we build everything.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Will it be SEO-friendly? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Every website we build includes solid SEO foundations — proper structure, meta tags, fast load times, and local schema markup. This alone brings faster traffic, leads, and conversions compared to a poorly built site. For deeper results, we also offer a dedicated SEO service that goes far beyond what is built into the website itself. We will let you know what makes sense for your goals.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Can you add booking, forms, or e-commerce features? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Yes. We integrate appointment booking systems, lead capture forms, payment gateways, e-commerce stores, and CRM tools. Tell us what your business needs and we will build it in.</p>
                </details>
              </div>

              <!-- Panel 3: Ownership & Hosting -->
              <div id="faqpanel3" class="faq-panel">
                <details class="faq-item" open>
                  <summary>Will I own my website when it is done? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">100%. Once the project is complete and paid for, everything is yours — code, content, domain, and hosting account. No lock-in, no platform fees owed to us.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Do I need to sort out hosting and a domain myself? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">We handle the full setup for you. We recommend the right hosting for your site type, configure everything, and connect your domain. You do not need to touch any of it unless you want to.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Can I update the website myself after launch? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Yes. We hand you a short walkthrough showing how to make common changes yourself. And for anything else, your first year of maintenance is on us.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Are there any extra costs for tools or plugins? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">We normally build without locking you into specific paid tools. However, some projects require premium plugins or third-party add-ons to deliver a feature you specifically need — such as a booking system or payment gateway. In those cases the cost of those tools is covered by the client and will always be communicated clearly before we proceed.</p>
                </details>
              </div>

              <!-- Panel 4: Pricing & Payment -->
              <div id="faqpanel4" class="faq-panel">
                <details class="faq-item" open>
                  <summary>How much does a website cost? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Every website is different. Pricing depends on the complexity, size, and your specific requirements and instructions. We provide a clear, itemized quote after your free strategy call — so you know exactly what you are paying for before committing to anything.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>How does payment work? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">We split the project into three payments: 50% upfront to start the project, 25% before we enter the final phase, and 25% on launch day after all final touches are complete.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Are there any ongoing costs after launch? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">The only recurring costs are hosting and your domain name — both of which you control directly. We cover maintenance, security updates, and small content edits one at a time free for your first 12 months.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Do you offer payment plans for larger projects? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">For projects of $2,000 and above we offer a structured payment plan using the same 50/25/25 split, making it easier to manage the investment as the project progresses.</p>
                </details>
              </div>

              <!-- Panel 5: AI & How We Build -->
              <div id="faqpanel5" class="faq-panel">
                <details class="faq-item" open>
                  <summary>Do you use AI in your web design process? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Yes — and it is one of the reasons we work faster and smarter than traditional agencies. We use AI tools across design, content structure, code generation, and SEO to accelerate every stage of the build without cutting corners on quality. You get the speed of AI with the judgment and strategy of a human team behind every decision.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Does AI mean my website will look generic? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Not at all. AI handles the repetitive and technical work — we handle the strategy, creative direction, and everything that makes your brand unique. Every website is custom to your business, AI just helps us get there faster.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Will my website be future-proof with AI search? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Yes. We build every site with clean structure, schema markup, and content architecture that performs in both traditional Google search and AI-powered search platforms like ChatGPT and Perplexity. As search evolves, your site is already built for what comes next.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Can you build AI features into my website? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Absolutely. We can integrate AI-powered chat, lead qualification tools, smart booking systems, and automated follow-up flows. If you have a specific idea, bring it to your strategy call and we will tell you exactly what is possible.</p>
                </details>
              </div>

              <!-- Panel 6: Results & Support -->
              <div id="faqpanel6" class="faq-panel">
                <details class="faq-item" open>
                  <summary>Will my website actually bring in new clients? <span class="faq-icon"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="1" y1="6" x2="11" y2="6"/></svg></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">That is the entire point of how we build. Every layout, call to action, and page structure is designed around conversion — not just aesthetics. Results depend on your market and traffic, but your site will be built to convert from day one.</p>
